o work with all stakeholders to support citizen generated data in order to improve on the quality of statistical information, enhance dissemination and accessibility of statistics at the county level. H.E. Prof Kivutha Kibwana Governor, Makueni County CCoouunnttyy SSttaattiissttiiccaall AAbbssttrraacctt,, 22002200 xxii":null,
